    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Games or toys that are modelled on pinball machines but tailored to children. These may consist of a rectangular sloped box in which balls or marbles are shot up upwards from a sprung lever.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
